narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Not well organized. A lot of things can be taught in a professional seminar. For example: 1. How to write a proposal (observation)? 2. How to apply for a scholarship? 3. How to give a public talk? 4. How to give a professional conference talk? 5. How to give a job talk? 6. How to present your work in a professional poster? 6. Tips and ideas about how to write a paper. 7. How to do outreach? ... etc. These topics are really useful for graduate students and I hope they can be incorporated into the course.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Not really, I think the structure & content of the course needs to be revised.
